<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">خامسًا:</span> مصنفاته في الفقه:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ - الأَصْلَحُ فِي إِمَامَةِ غَيْرِ الأفصَح.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٢ - تِحْفَةُ المُسْتَرِيض بِمَسْأَلَةِ المَحِيْض.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٣ - التَّمَتُّعُ عَلَى مَذْهَبِ الحَنَفِيَّة.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٤ - التَّنْبِيْهُ لِصِفَةِ التّمَتُّعِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٥ - خَبَرٌ فِي <span class="c1">"الْحَجّ"</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٦ - خَبَرُ الثَّبْت بِصِيَامِ السَّبْت.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٧ - الخِصَالُ المُكَفِّرَةِ لِلْذُنُوبِ <span class="c1">"المقدمة والمؤخرة"</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٨ - رِسَالَةٌ فِي تَعَدُّدِ الجُمُعَةِ ببلدة واحدة.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٩ - شَرْحُ <span class="c1">"الْإِرْشَاد"</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١٠ - شَرْحُ <span class="c1">"الرَّوْضَة"</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>١١ - شَرْحُ مَنَاسِكِ <span class="c1">"الْمِنْهَاج"</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١٢ - التَّعْلِيْقُ النَّافِع في النكت على <span class="c1">"جمع الجوامع"</span> لابن السبكي.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">سادسًا:</span> مصنفاته في علوم اللغة:<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>١ - تَحْرِيرُ <span class="c1">"مُقَدِّمة فِي العرُوضِ"</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>٢ - تَقرِيبُ الغَرِيبِ الوَاقِعُ فِي الصَّحِيْحِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>٣ - السَّهْلُ المَنِيْع في شَواهِدِ البَدِيْعِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>٤ - غِرَاسُ الأَسَاس.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>٥ - دِيوَانُ شعري الكبير.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>٦ - السَّبْعَةُ السَّيَّارَة النيران.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>٧ - ضَوْءُ الشِّهَاب.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>٨ - قَذَى العَيْنِ مِنْ نَظمِ عَذَابِ البَيْنِ.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>